{"type":null,"faqId":48006,"title":"手势控制","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.3784722in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4027778in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>使用手势控制，可以让您通过简单的动作控制手机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177674\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“手势控制”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>在“手势控制”界面，点击某一选项，启用对应动作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>“翻转”：来电、闹钟或计时器响铃或振动时，翻转手机可以静音并停止振动。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177675\" style=\"width:1.45625in;height:1.2493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>“摇一摇”：长按主屏幕空白区域，即可进入主屏幕编辑状态。在主屏幕编辑状态下，摇晃手机可以将散落在屏幕各个位置的图标瞬间排列整齐。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177676\" style=\"width:1.45625in;height:1.2493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>“双击”：屏幕关闭状态下，快速双击屏幕有效区可以唤醒屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177677\" style=\"width:1.2576389in;height:1.2493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>“画字母”：屏幕关闭状态下，画字母打开对应应用程序。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177678\" style=\"width:0.9465278in;height:1.25in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1090,"faqType":"开始使用","useful":6,"unUseful":6,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3592","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Getting-know-phone","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598085000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":182,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}